  A & r1 & 1 & 10 \\
   & r2 & 2 & 20 \\
   & r3 & 3 & 30 \\
  \midrule\addlinespace[2.5pt]
  Sum & --- & 6 & 60 \\
  B & r4 & 4 & 40 \\
   & r5 & 5 & 50 \\
   & r6 & 6 & 60 \\
  \midrule\addlinespace[2.5pt]
  Sum & --- & 15 & 150 \\
  '''
